  "remarks": "\nAL-SAYYAD COMPANY FOR GUARDING AND PROTECTION SERVICES LTD is an involved person under the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 because they are engaging in and providing support for actions or policies that have destabilised Ukraine or undermined or threatened the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine by recruiting fighters and mercenaries in Syria to fight alongside Russian forces in Ukraine. \n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
